Moving first group of four elements (First
elements of 1st row, last row, 1st column
and last column) of first cycle in counter
clockwise.
 4  2  3 16
 5  6  7 8
 9 10 11 12
 1 14  15 13

Moving next group of four elements of
first cycle in counter clockwise
 4  8  3 16
 5  6  7  15
